<body>
    <h1>Mediterranean Street Cart Bowl Bar</h1>
    <p><strong>Description:</strong> A customizable Mediterranean-inspired street cart bowl bar featuring a variety of proteins, toppings, and sauces for a delicious and interactive meal experience.</p>
    <img src="https://joshelledge.github.io/Recipes/mediterranean_street_cart_bowl_bar.webp" alt="Mediterranean Street Cart Bowl Bar" style="width:100%; max-width:500px;">
    <h2>Ingredients</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>Yellow rice or couscous</li>
        <li>Grilled chicken shawarma</li>
        <li>Falafel</li>
        <li>Warm chickpeas</li>
        <li>Cucumber and tomato salad</li>
        <li>Grilled zucchini and eggplant</li>
        <li>Pickled red onions</li>
        <li>Garlic yogurt sauce</li>
        <li>Tahini sauce</li>
        <li>Harissa sauce</li>
        <li>Hummus</li>
        <li>Feta cheese</li>
        <li>Kalamata olives</li>
        <li>Pita chips</li>
        <li>Toasted pine nuts</li>
        <li>Fresh parsley and mint</li>
    </ul>
    <h2>Instructions</h2>
    <ol>
        <li>Cook the base: Prepare yellow rice or couscous according to package instructions.</li>
        <li>Grill proteins: Season chicken with shawarma spices and grill until golden. Prepare falafel or warm chickpeas in olive oil with spices.</li>
        <li>Prepare sauces: Mix garlic yogurt, tahini sauce, and harissa.</li>
        <li>Chop and prepare veggies: Dice cucumbers, tomatoes, and pickled red onions. Grill zucchini and eggplant.</li>
        <li>Arrange extras: Crumble feta, toast pine nuts, and prep pita chips.</li>
        <li>Serve: Arrange ingredients buffet-style and let guests build their bowls.</li>
    </ol>
